					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span><a href="https://youtu.be/JYOTqexoje4?t=180">*CRUNCH*</a></span></h2> </div> <hr /> <p>I've had this idea on the backburner for a while, but I've decided to kick it up front to fuel the sparks of <span style="color: purple">Arcadia</span>. This article is mainly inspired by stories I've heard about roach infestations and how they can and will spread to any unoccupied space. While I may appreciate them scientifically and aesthetically, I chose to do so from a distance.</p> <p>Huge thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596991655" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4894577&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596991655" alt="Laneous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4894577)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" >Laneous</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1596991655" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span> for critting this while it was in development.</p> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/the-bread-box">Other Articles of Mine</a></p> </div> 
				 	]]>
